OL,3,C'Slap in the face' as Irish Justice
OL,4,CMinister refuses to meet Creeslough
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FFamilies of those killed in the
OL,8,FCreeslough explosion have hit out at
OL,9,Fthe Irish Justice Minister for
OL,10,Frejecting a request to meet with them.
OL,12,FFour men, three women and three young
OL,13,Fpeople, aged between five and 59, died
OL,14,Fin the blast on the afternoon of
OL,15,FOctober 7, 2022 in the Co Donegal
OL,16,Fvillage.
OL,18,FRelatives campaigning for a public
OL,19,Finquiry requested a meeting with
OL,20,FMinister Jim O'Callaghan but described
OL,21,Fhis refusal as a "slap in the face".
OL,26,@}D@ROU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
