FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772223642
OL,3,C'Slap in the face' as Irish Justice
OL,4,CMinister refuses to meet Creeslough
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FIn December, Minister O'Callaghan met
OL,8,Fwith families to hear their concerns
OL,9,Fbut declined a further meeting to
OL,10,F"allow criminal proceedings to be
OL,11,Fcompleted".
OL,13,FThe 10 victims were Robert Garwe and
OL,14,Fhis five-year-old daughter Shauna
OL,15,FFlanagan-Garwe, Catherine O'Donnell
OL,16,Fand her 13-year-old son James
OL,17,FMonaghan, Celtic fan Martin McGill,
OL,18,FJames O'Flaherty from Sydney,
OL,19,FAustralia, shop worker Martina Martin
OL,20,Fand carpenter Hugh "Hughie" Kelly.
OL,26,@|D@TOU|D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772223642
OL,3,C'Slap in the face' as Irish Justice
OL,4,CMinister refuses to meet Creeslough
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FDonna Harper's 14-year-old daughter
OL,8,FLeona Harper also died.
OL,10,FShe described the Creeslough explosion
OL,11,Fas "one of the biggest things in the
OL,12,Fhistory of the state" and asked "why
OL,13,Fis the government not talking to the
OL,14,Ffamilies?"
OL,16,F"I was really shocked and hurt by it
OL,17,Fas well, that there was no plans to
OL,18,Fmeet anybody. I feel like it's a
OL,19,Fcomplete slap in the face."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772223642
OL,3,C'Slap in the face' as Irish Justice
OL,4,CMinister refuses to meet Creeslough
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,F24-year-old fashion student Jessica
OL,8,FGallagher was also a victim of the
OL,9,Fblast.
OL,11,FHer sister Shauna Marie Gallagher has
OL,12,Fexpressed her anger.
OL,14,F"It's shocking, but not shocking at
OL,15,Fthe same time. It really feels like
OL,16,Fwe're not being acknowledged by the
OL,17,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772223642
OL,3,C'Slap in the face' as Irish Justice
OL,4,CMinister refuses to meet Creeslough
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,F"None of us are expecting the minister
OL,8,Fto all of a sudden solve the case or
OL,9,Fto interfere in any way with the
OL,10,Fcriminal investigation, but to not
OL,11,Feven acknowledge us as a group is
OL,12,Fquite insulting."
OL,14,FIn a letter to one of the victims,
OL,15,Fseen by UTV, a spokesperson for the
OL,16,Fminister said it is important that the
OL,17,Fcriminal Garda investigation is
OL,18,F"progressed and not impeded or
OL,19,Fjeopardised in any way".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772223642
OL,3,C'Slap in the face' as Irish Justice
OL,4,CMinister refuses to meet Creeslough
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FThey said: "The criminal
OL,8,Finvestigation, combined with the
OL,9,Finvestigations by the relevant
OL,10,Fregulatory bodies and the coroner's
OL,11,Finquest, is best placed to provide the
OL,12,Fnecessary answer about the dreadful
OL,13,Fevents in Cresslough."
OL,15,F"Please be assured that completion of
OL,16,Fthe active criminal investigation,
OL,17,Faccountability, and justice is the
OL,18,Ffocus of An Garda Siochana and the
OL,19,FMinister," they added.
